0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"learning curve有d高&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"其實唔算有啲高<br />\n係地獄級難度<br />\n但稍為上手後，根本番唔到轉頭<br />\n我依家都係用咗大半年，效率高過以前好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:27:20.000Z","msg":"好似幾吸引，你一開始係點入手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T17:36:45.000Z","msg":"當初用emacs 純粹係因為買咗個hhkb <br />\n覺得唔好浪費走去學<br />\n就喺vim 同emacs 之間選擇<br />\n而我幾鍾意Mac 就揀咗emacs 開始<br />\n（後來發覺完全唔關事嘅）<br />\n<br />\nEmacs 有好多開局<br />\n有啲人recommend 用啲人地set好嘅starter kit<br />\n我試過幾種starter kit <br />\n個人覺得完全由零開始比較好<br />\n因為咁先清楚自己做緊乜<br />\nYouTube 有好多tutorial<br />\n我建議超過二十分鐘嘅完全冇必要睇<br />\n太浪費時間<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果你用windows 嘅話，可以skip 咗emacs呢個option<br />\n因為好多功能都冇咗<br />\n用Mac 或Linux 嘅不失為個好選擇<br />\n但你要將成個workflow搬入emacs 先有最大效率<br />\n包括平時用嘅IDE，git ，terminal等等<br />\n<br />\n有機會我可能另開個post分享下我嘅經驗"},{"pid":"fdfa9735f485262838d2b00b5cc3558ed6dfaa1c","tid":2366062,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7eceb52586d481113ce61580ed8cc340e231746","tid":2366062,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdfa9735f485262838d2b00b5cc3558ed6dfaa1c","tid":2366062,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T17:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42891ad09fc0aa776b63e67aa353a2723521a75e","tid":2366062,"uid":46200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bc8c5fd689405353a24002a37cdabe2d6c5ba9d","tid":2366062,"uid":228679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb28a7edf478e0356d3b20d842098b73f8253496","tid":2366062,"uid":46200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d359ebb0d71b57b77caf44d04540c9536be6bff","tid":2366062,"uid":254681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"learning curve有d高&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"其實唔算有啲高<br />\n係地獄級難度<br />\n但稍為上手後，根本番唔到轉頭<br />\n我依家都係用咗大半年，效率高過以前好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"Why not vim?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"我係用emacs 先嘅<br />\n之後都有試過vim<br />\n我個人覺得兩樣嘢唔可以相題並論<br />\nVim 嘅好處係lightweight，一般會喺terminal 裏面用<br />\n用熟咗兩者都會拋開其他text editor 幾條街<br />\nVim嘅問題係，佢係用嚟做text editing <br />\n用嚟寫extension 嘅language 冇emacs 咁好<br />\n用vim 嘅人嘅workflow會喺terminal 切出切入 因為要用其他command<br />\n<br />\nEmacs 就係一大堆keybindings 喺emacs裏面做嘢<br />\n真正用家幾乎唔會離開emacs<br />\n本身嘅Operating system 變到好似只係emacs 嘅boot loader <br />\n<br />\nVim係一個無上限嘅text editor<br />\nEmacs係一個無上限嘅software ，咁啱入面有個text editor<br />\nVim 做到嘅emacs都做到，甚至你可以用vim 嘅keybinding<br />\n唔考慮portability 嘅住家毒撚，睇唔出vim有咩優勢"},{"pid":"d665b61cd3fb76c4fcda400287af3a735bf307f0","tid":2366062,"uid":64662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a8e91a5a08612c84785276695788b671c10b5116","tid":2366062,"uid":294342,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:35:00.000Z","msg":"notepad++"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:26:37.000Z","msg":"New 12 New 23 New 34<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a8962fb66e69eb2d2300a5d9e129ab49c45066","tid":2366062,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:16:18.000Z","msg":"evernote"},{"pid":"b186547f12f15f2a474c16aeaec3d8e46179a6a4","tid":2366062,"uid":54697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"hackmd"},{"pid":"e5ccfeaae94344e9a34513898ada7336ef25f497","tid":2366062,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7eceb52586d481113ce615